data.description: 6.5% 7/1 ARM financing available for qualified buyers under contract by December 31, 2023. Fantastic cul-de-sac location just steps away from community park! Lots of space in this 3-step ranch! Over 2400 square feet of living space not including finished lower level. The beautiful kitchen boasts oak cabinets, pantry, skylight, custom backsplash, quartz counters, crown molding & oversized tile; Spacious family room with cozy fireplace, crown molding & laminate flooring; Sun-filled living room with bay window; Double door entry to the formal dining room with gleaming hardwood flooring; Powder room with decorative shiplap wall; Desirable main level laundry; Amazing sunroom that is heated & cooled, overlooking the large paver patio & fenced yard with gardens; Solid 6 panel oak doors throughout; The master suite offers a walk-in closet & private bath with oversized tub, separate shower & skylight; All bedrooms are generous sized; The finished, look-out English basement offers a recreation room, 4th bedroom & full bath that's perfect for related living; Extra deep. 2 1/2 car garage.
